{"tid":1930681,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"閉起雙眼你最掛念誰 眼睛張開身邊竟是誰","createTime":"2020-03-17T17:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T04:26:28.000Z","uid":245850,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cb611ac0ff19f7c98e6b1a43faa396b74d803880","tid":1930681,"uid":245850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:10:05.000Z","msg":"我好中意你 我好愛你 我好掛住你 我對唔住你<br />\n<br />\n同你分開左兩個幾月喇，以前你用晒所有時間黎陪我，我冇好好珍惜之餘仲成日發你脾氣，我知你失望到唔想再繼續落去，我明白你擔心d咩先離開我。<br />\n<br />\n好多謝你陪左我咁耐，雖然你唔太識做人男朋友，但我都感受到係e一年你已經盡晒力咁去學。對唔住，我嘅自私傷害埋你，回憶總是美好的，曾經相愛過就夠喇。<br />\n<br />\n記住要對你以後既女朋友好過我3000倍啊<br />\n最後工作加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都會好好努力move on<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b7218d5dd8c43a05a74a8007ca258809905bfe","tid":1930681,"uid":188129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4c80f821f808222c45b36954f8a6bc184c13c1","tid":1930681,"uid":63639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:19:25.000Z","msg":"關首歌咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e73bad68a739c7d2f2af7c36a3056348c7f47f","tid":1930681,"uid":245850,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"dc4c80f821f808222c45b36954f8a6bc184c13c1","tid":1930681,"uid":63639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:19:25.000Z","msg":"關首歌咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:21:46.000Z","msg":"因為我有現任"},{"pid":"00e5f3143e523cbe7d0c8058406b654a9e653a83","tid":1930681,"uid":63639,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"00e73bad68a739c7d2f2af7c36a3056348c7f47f","tid":1930681,"uid":245850,"like":0,"dislike":